#### How Each Table is Used

| Table | Written By | Read By | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| `soil_data` | `POST /predict` (backend) | `GET /history` (JOIN) | Stores raw soil parameter readings |
| `predictions` | `POST /predict` (backend) | `GET /history` (JOIN) | Stores ML output (quality, crops, tips) |
| `farmers` | `POST /api/verify-otp` | `POST /api/verify-otp` | Farmer registration & login tracking |
| `otp_store` | `POST /api/send-otp` | `POST /api/verify-otp` | Temporary OTP storage (rate-limited, 2-min expiry) |
| `model_metrics` | (unused currently) | — | Reserved for storing model versions |

